# Valid character definition tests
# Full definition syntax: char = expression

# Simple definitions
明 = ⿰日月
林 = ⿰木木
森 = ⿱木⿰木木

# Definition with code point (CSDL-U style)
U+660E = ⿰日月
U+6797 = ⿰木木

# Multiple definitions in sequence
明 = ⿰日月
暗 = ⿰日音
曉 = ⿰日堯
晴 = ⿰日青

# Definition referencing prior definition (if permitted)
相 = ⿰木目
想 = ⿱相心

# Surround variants
國 = ⿴囗或
園 = ⿴囗袁
圖 = ⿴囗啚

# Complex expressions in definitions
鬱 = ⿳⿲木缶木冖⿺⿻彡⿱ム⿻コ⿱⿲丿丿丿⿰彡彡

# Edge: single character operands only
好 = ⿰女子
